#Text=Wikinews interviews Ruth Bryant White , independent candidate for US President
#Text=Tuesday , February 19 , 2008

#Text=While nearly all coverage of the 2008 Presidential election has focused on the Democratic and Republican candidates , the race for the White House also includes independents and third party candidates .
#Text=These parties represent a variety of views that may not be acknowledged by the major party platforms .
#Text=Wikinews has impartially reached out to these candidates , throughout the campaign .
#Text=We now interview independent Presidential candidate Ruth Bryant White , an ordained Christian minister , author , and homemaker .
#Text=Interview
#Text=Why do you want to be President ?
#Text=I do n’t , but I will serve for the betterment of our Country .
#Text=I love my country
#Text=I do n’t like politics .
#Text=I seem to be the best qualified candidate besides Mike Huckabee , whom I would gladly work with to run this country .
#Text=I would love to be Co-President with someone who takes care of business and is not trying to become a Washington Insider .
#Text=I believe we can clean up the mess in Washington .
#Text=We ’re the only two that can in my humble opinion .
#Text=Nobody knows what ’s happening in Middle America .
#Text=The so-called front-runners can only rely on their advisors .
#Text=I know what ’s happening , because I ’m a part of Middle America , I know and see the hurts and the issues first hand .
#Text=Have you ever run for political office before ?
#Text=No , but I ’ve worked for the United States Air Force and I ’ve worked for the Veteran ’s Administration
#Text=Have you ever been a member of a political party , other than the one you 're currently in ?
#Text=No , and I would n’t join one now , especially with the cronyism and fundraising a Candidate has to do for a party instead doing the job we pay them to do i. e to run our country .
#Text=If this was private Industry most of them would be fired by now fordoing a poor job of making sure our country is never depending on other countries for anything .

#Text=However I ’m a mother and grandmother and I see first hand how our country is going down the tubes and I want to do everything I can to save it , so I put my Barbeque pit away and my lounge chair and said I Love my Country enough to do whatever I can to save us .
#Text=Have you ever campaigned for another political candidate ?
#Text=No , but I would for Mike Huckabee if he and I were not both running for President .
#Text=What is your current job ?
#Text=I ’m running For President Full Time , I ’m a Certificated Christian Counselor , an Ordained Minister , an Author , Public Speaker , and Homemaker .
#Text=What skills or ideas do or previous positions , you bring from this position that will benefit the Oval Office ?
